snippet.title: Infamous Duck Ball | Trailer
snippet.description:
Infamous Duck Ball is a chaotic online co-op & competitive game for 2 to 4 players. You play as ducks who cannot swim. Make use of the balloon fish to destroy other ducks' safety rings (and their holiday)!

This trailer is edited by my teammate Julia Wang :)
